{"tid":1723964,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[爦炒] 二○一九年九月三十日財務狀況為954億港元赤字","createTime":"2019-11-15T10:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T16:24:36.000Z","uid":121001,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"cf86b7a45edffcf36cf92c04b26116e95399c9e3","tid":1723964,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:38:05.000Z","msg":"小弟得閒得制上左政府網睇下今年政府既財務狀況<br />\n發覺政府做野真係好有效率  好心依班問責官員搞一件事搞左五個月都搞唔掂就妥協  危機處理真係世界級  香港經濟真係比佢地搞衰哂<br />\n以下係今年一月到九月三十日既財務狀況  由六月開始已經有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>148億港元赤字</strong></span>  去到九月三十日已經係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">954億港元赤字</span></strong><br />\n十月(應該十一月三十日)  十一月(應該十二月三十一日)財務狀況都<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲未出</span></strong><br />\n運動到依一刻都<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲未完</span></strong><br />\n依個情況再咁落去, 而財政儲備在九月三十日為10,755億港元<br />\n小弟估計十月份既報告應該少過一萬億港元<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">爦炒之路不遠了</span></strong></span><br />\n有冇account, finance 巴打補充下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f2CkYz7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff2CkYz7.png&h=a095eaec&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M4C1H1O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM4C1H1O.png&h=f3230e8d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nk5FYz8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNk5FYz8.png&h=8fe845f3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wOKjuGP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwOKjuGP.png&h=3143ef4b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ij5On1P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fij5On1P.png&h=547ccf7e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/46qq9GP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F46qq9GP.png&h=c6b531c9&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z2gYLfa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ2gYLfa.png&h=52bd2ca7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/codL9GQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcodL9GQ.png&h=b183f164&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NDjC0Ov.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDjC0Ov.png&h=511dc8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.try.gov.hk/cinternet/chpubl_acco_monfinancial.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.try.gov.hk%2Fcinternet%2Fchpubl_acco_monfinancial.html&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYTvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=87ef6521\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.try.gov.hk/cinternet/chpubl_acco_monfinancial.html</a>"},{"pid":"8b7d5e6a477f7241da8225318228ea12ef5328e0","tid":1723964,"uid":77473,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:38:55.000Z","msg":"成績表<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897c2787ef5066492b86c8c91448282c30f83136","tid":1723964,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be32589857d0321fe372da2816230efe1cb6c34","tid":1723964,"uid":177213,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8b7d5e6a477f7241da8225318228ea12ef5328e0","tid":1723964,"uid":77473,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:38:55.000Z","msg":"成績表<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:41:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">過3</span></span><span style=\"font